# Copy to `.env` and fill in. Never commit real secrets. The `.env` file is
# git-ignored. The dependency-free demo, the test suite, AND the default STAC
# data path need NONE of these — STAC (Earth Search) is auth-free.

# Optional: Earth Engine Cloud project id. Only needed for the OPTIONAL geemap /
# Earth Engine path (eets.gee, notebooks/02_geemap_change.ipynb). Get a free one
# at https://console.cloud.google.com and run `earthengine authenticate` once.
EARTHENGINE_PROJECT=your-earth-engine-project-id
